headline: Jacobs and AtkinsRéalis Appointed National Highways' Environmental and Sustainability Technical Partner
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J), in joint venture with AtkinsRéalis, has been appointed by National Highways in the U.K. to provide essential environmental and sustainability technical services to support the organization's strategy to reduce carbon emissions, enhance biodiversity and climate resilience, and support community wellbeing.
